history.content:
Want to have your voice heard by EECS faculty, staff, and the Chairs?

The Center for Student Affairs, HKN and other EECS student organizations have composed the 2017-18 EECS Undergraduate Survey so you can provide input and feedback to our very own EECS Department. This is a great opportunity for you to make a real impact in your classes, student life, and campus culture.

Your thoughts will reach faculty and will be used to help improve the department and the community!

In addition, once you complete the survey, you can choose to enter a prize drawing to win one of fifteen (15) $10 Amazon gift cards!

Your response is completely anonymous. We encourage you to respond openly and honestly!

The survey can be saved, and returned to for completion later.

The survey is available here:

2017-18 EECS Undergraduate Survey
history.subject: Complete our big annual survey about the EECS/CS experience! (undergrads only)
